NK041(di)045:1: // bar do'i smon lam dgongs gcig rgya mtsho zhes bya ba bzhugs /
NK041(di)045:2: bar do'i smon lam dgongs gcig rgya mtsho ni /
NK041(di)045:3: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK041(di)045:4: bdag nyid bla ma rin po che //
NK041(di)045:5: mgon med bdag la thugs rjes gzigs //
NK041(di)045:6: ma rig 'thibs pos non pa bdag /
NK041(di)045:7: 'khor tshe thog ma med pa nas //
NK041(di)045:8: las nyon sdig pas zil gyis non //
NK041(di)045:9: bla ma brnyas shing spun la khros //
NK041(di)045:10: dam tshig sdom pa'i gnas kun yang //
NK041(di)045:11: nyes spyod chen po'i g.yang sar ltung //
NK041(di)045:12: ma 'tshal bzhin du nongs pa kun //
NK041(di)045:13: de ring gnong 'gyod drag pos bshags //
NK041(di)045:14: sngon chad khyed kyi bka' las 'das //
NK041(di)045:15: de lta'i sdig ltung ma byang bar //
NK041(di)045:16: 'jig rten pha rol song gyur na //
NK041(di)045:17: dmyal me bzod dka' nges par bsreg /
NK041(di)045:18: de tshe bdag nyid 'dor phod dam /
NK041(di)045:19: thog mtha' med pa'i 'khrul gzhi ni //
NK041(di)045:20: lung ma bstan gyi chos nyid nas //
NK041(di)045:21: kun 'byung ma rig gdon chen dang //
NK041(di)045:22: 'grogs pa'i rang bzhin skye gnas kyi //
NK041(di)045:23: bar dor chos ldan dal 'byor lus //
NK041(di)045:24: thob nas bla ma mnyes byed cing //
NK041(di)045:25: thos bsam sgom pa'i shes rab la //
NK041(di)045:26: brten nas nges 'byung byang chub sems //
NK041(di)045:27: phyin drug lam mchog bsnyen par shog /
NK041(di)045:28: dus kyis nyen te 'gro ba la //
NK041(di)045:29: 'chi ka'i bar do zhes bya ste //
NK041(di)045:30: de tshe 'chi rkyen ngan pa dang //
NK041(di)045:31: gnad gcod drag po mi 'byung zhing //
NK041(di)045:32: dbyings dang rig pa bse ba yis //
NK041(di)045:34: gdod ma'i gzhi la grol bar shog /
NK041(di)045:35: gal te goms pa'i stobs chung na //
NK041(di)045:36: sgo brgyad bkag nas tshang bug dbye //
NK041(di)045:37: rnam shes rlung zhon gdams pa yis //
NK041(di)045:39: mkha' spyod rig 'dzin gnas thob shog /
NK041(di)045:40: de ltar byang chub sems dpa' yi //
NK041(di)045:41: 'pho lugs mngon du ma gyur na //
NK041(di)045:42: sa la sa thim ldang mi nus //
NK041(di)045:43: chu la chu thim kha snar chu //
NK041(di)045:44: me la me thim kha sna skam //
NK041(di)045:45: rlung thim dbugs ngar yan lag phra //
NK041(di)045:46: smig sbren gyen ldog du ba dang //
NK041(di)045:47: smig rgyu me khyer mar me 'bar //
NK041(di)045:48: rlung lnga bros pa'i byed las kyis //
NK041(di)045:49: khyab bya 'byung ba'i khams lnga dang //
NK041(di)045:50: khyab byed ye shes thig le'i dpyid //
NK041(di)045:51: rgyab gyes yul lnga yid shes la //
NK041(di)045:52: thim par phyogs tshe 'di snang la //
NK041(di)045:53: zhen chags gdung ba mi skye zhing //
NK041(di)045:54: bla ma'i gdams ngag dran par shog /
NK041(di)045:55: rigs pa rtsa thig rlung gsum gyi //
NK041(di)045:56: tshogs pa gyes pa'i rten 'brel las //
NK041(di)045:57: phra ba snang mched thob gsum gyi //
NK041(di)045:58: thim tshul dkar cha thur babs te //
NK041(di)045:59: snying stobs las byung 'dod chags kyi //
NK041(di)045:60: rtog pa 'gag dang lhan cig par //
NK041(di)045:61: rnam shes snang ba la thim pas //
NK041(di)045:62: ston gnam zla 'od kyis slong lta'i //
NK041(di)045:65: mun pa gti mug tu bshad pas bcos bslad ma byed cig /
NK041(di)045:66: dkar lam rang ngo shes par shog /
NK041(di)045:67: de bzhin dmar cha gyen du ldog /
NK041(di)045:68: rdul las byung ba'i zhe sdang 'gag /
NK041(di)045:69: snang ba mched pa la thim pas //
NK041(di)045:70: skar khung nyi zhur kyis slong lta'i //
NK041(di)045:71: dmar lam rang ngo shes par shog /
NK041(di)045:72: khu rdul snying gar phrad pa las //
NK041(di)045:73: mun can las byung gti mug 'gag /
NK041(di)045:74: mched pa nyer thob la thim pas //
NK041(di)045:75: ston gnam smag gis slong ba lta'i //
NK041(di)045:76: nag lam shar nas brgyal ba la //
NK041(di)045:77: phyogs tshe dran pa'i sgron me yis //
NK041(di)045:79: gdod ma'i dbyings su sangs rgyas shog /
NK041(di)045:80: gal te dran pa'i stobs zhan pas //
NK041(di)045:81: brgyal te sems med skabs gyur na //
NK041(di)045:82: kun gzhi chos dbyings la sad nas //
NK041(di)045:83: dngas gsal rtog pa med pa yi //
NK041(di)045:85: de ltar chos sku'i bsre ba yis //
NK041(di)045:86: gdod ma'i nang dbyings ma zin na //
NK041(di)045:87: shin tu phra ba'i rlung sems che //
NK041(di)045:88: lugs ldog nye bar thob pa las //
NK041(di)045:89: mched pa'i snang ba chos nyid kyi //
NK041(di)045:90: bar de gzhi dbyings ka dag klong //
NK041(di)045:91: khregs chod lta bas mngon gyur zhing //
NK041(di)045:92: gzhi snang yin lugs 'od gsal ni //
NK041(di)045:93: snang ba thams cad 'od lnga ru //
NK041(di)045:94: za 'og bkram pa ltar shar tshe //
NK041(di)045:95: thod rgal goms pa'i nye rgyu las //
NK041(di)045:96: rang snang rang bzhin med par shes //
NK041(di)045:97: chos nyid cig char zad par shog /
NK041(di)045:99: thim nas rigs brgya'i snang ba shar //
NK041(di)045:100: sgra yis 'jigs shing zer gyis sngang //
NK041(di)045:101: sku yi snang bas skrag gyur na //
NK041(di)045:102: seng ge'i gsob ltar mtshang rig nas //
NK041(di)045:103: bag mi tsha ba'i gdeng thob shog /
NK041(di)045:104: bsam gtan gyis ni zhag lnga la //
NK041(di)045:105: rgyal ba rigs lnga'i zhal mthong tshe //
NK041(di)045:108: sku yang rang la thim pa yis //
NK041(di)045:110: ma pang bu 'jug ltar grol shog /
NK041(di)045:111: de bzhin zung 'jug ye shes la //
NK041(di)045:112: thim pas 'od snang thig le can //
NK041(di)045:113: ye shes bzhi sbyor snang ba ni //
NK041(di)045:114: rdo rje sems dpa'i khong seng lam //
NK041(di)045:115: snang tshe rig pa rang sa zin //
NK041(di)045:116: ye shes lhun grub la thim pas //
NK041(di)045:117: sku dang ye shes thugs rje 'od //
NK041(di)045:118: mtha' grol gnyis med dag ma dag /
NK041(di)045:119: lhun grub ye shes chen po'i sgo //
NK041(di)045:121: 'jug ldog rig pa'i rang rtsal du //
NK041(di)045:122: shar ba gzhi las ma g.yos pa'i //
NK041(di)045:123: gzhi snang chen por yid ches shog /
NK041(di)045:124: de yang bskyed rim la goms na //
NK041(di)045:125: rlung sems tsam gyi lus de nyid //
NK041(di)045:126: mtshan dpe rdzogs pa'i yi dam gyi //
NK041(di)045:127: lha skur mngon byang lngas chub pa //
NK041(di)045:128: bar dor longs sku'i bsre ba yis //
NK041(di)045:129: sgyu ma'i sku ru lang bar shog /
NK041(di)045:130: gang zhig mos pas spyod rnams kyang //
NK041(di)045:131: rjes dran lnga dang mngon shes drug /
NK041(di)045:132: mi brjed gzungs kyis dbugs 'byin nas //
NK041(di)045:133: bla ma dran nas rjes 'dzin shog /
NK041(di)045:134: yi dam dran nas zhal mthong zhing //
NK041(di)045:135: lta ba dang ni bsam gtan dang //
NK041(di)045:136: skye gnas man ngag dran par shog /
NK041(di)045:137: de bzhin sngon gnas shes pa dang //
NK041(di)045:139: pha rol gyi ni sems shes dang //
NK041(di)045:140: snang ba lkog gyur shes pa dang //
NK041(di)045:141: rigs drug gnas rigs mthong zhing shes //
NK041(di)045:142: dbang po rnam dag mngon shes dang //
NK041(di)045:143: sngon chad thos so cog gis mtshon //
NK041(di)045:144: chos kyi rnam grangs tshad med pa //
NK041(di)045:145: rgyud la 'char ba'i mi brjed gzungs //
NK041(di)045:146: thob tshe nges par grol ba'i gnad //
NK041(di)045:147: stong nyid spros bral ka dag gi //
NK041(di)045:148: rig pa cer mthong rang thog tu //
NK041(di)045:149: ngo shes thag chod gdeng thob shog /
NK041(di)045:150: mdor na chos nyid bar ma do'i //
NK041(di)045:151: rnam par dpyad na mtha' med kyang //
NK041(di)045:152: dpyod mkhan nyid la tshur brtags na //
NK041(di)045:153: gang du'ang grub pa med pa la //
NK041(di)045:154: med do snyom pa'ang rang grol ba //
NK041(di)045:155: 'di ni gdod ma'i grol sa ste //
NK041(di)045:156: gzhon nu bum pa'i sku thob nas //
NK041(di)045:157: lhun grub rtsal las sprul pa las //
NK041(di)045:159: gal te srid pa bar do la //
NK041(di)045:160: kha 'khyal ming bzhi lus pa can //
NK041(di)045:161: dbang po kun tshang yid kyi lus //
NK041(di)045:162: shi bar ngo shes dran pa gsal //
NK041(di)045:163: rnam grol sa dang skye gnas la //
NK041(di)045:164: thogs pa'i bya sgro rlung khyer ltar //
NK041(di)045:165: las rlung rjes 'gro nyam thag cing //
NK041(di)045:166: bred sngangs kyis gdungs bdun tshan re'i //
NK041(di)045:167: mtshams su 'chi ba'i sdug bsngal gyi //
NK041(di)045:168: tshor ba nyams myong skye gnas 'tshol //
NK041(di)045:169: de tshe rang bzhin sprul pa'i zhing //
NK041(di)045:170: mngon par dga' dang dpal ldan dang //
NK041(di)045:171: pad+ma brtsegs dang las rab grub //
NK041(di)045:172: dbus phyogs me ri 'bar ba ste //
NK041(di)045:173: rnam grol dbugs chen 'byin pa lnga'i //
NK041(di)045:174: dag zhing yid la goms byas nas //
NK041(di)045:175: gdon mi za bar bgrod par shog /
NK041(di)045:176: gal te rig pa'i rtsal dbang gis //
NK041(di)045:177: ma smin bden pa ma mthong na //
NK041(di)045:178: so so'i gnas rigs mngon gyur ram //
NK041(di)045:179: dmyal ba sdong dum yi dwags du //
NK041(di)045:180: mgo bo thur lta byol song khrag /
NK041(di)045:181: lha min kha char mgo yang 'drad //
NK041(di)045:182: lha mi dkar zhing gyen du 'greng //
NK041(di)045:183: 'dod lha yul la dga' gdung dang //
NK041(di)045:184: gzugs khams 'od la gzugs med ni //
NK041(di)045:185: ci yang med pa'i stong phyad la //
NK041(di)045:186: dga' gdung 'char zhing khyad par nga //
NK041(di)045:188: chags sdang bden med sbyong ba'am //
NK041(di)045:189: gsum pa'i dbang don nyams myong zhing //
NK041(di)045:190: skye gnas bzhi yi spyad gzhi dang //
NK041(di)045:191: sbyong byed goms pa'i bskyed rim gyis //
NK041(di)045:192: sngags la spyod pa'i rten can dang //
NK041(di)045:193: skye ba sprul sku'i bsre ba yis //
NK041(di)045:194: nying mtshams sbyor ba'i mthu thob shog /
NK041(di)045:195: smin byed dbang dang grol byed khrid //
NK041(di)045:196: bsrung bya dam tshig thob bya 'bras //
NK041(di)045:197: rnam pa bzhi ru bsre ba dang //
NK041(di)045:198: sgo gsum lha sngags chos nyid du //
NK041(di)045:199: 'pho ba'i gnad la ma goms na //
NK041(di)045:200: 'byung bzhi rlung gi byed las kyis //
NK041(di)045:201: shin tu 'jigs pa'i sgra bzhi dang //
NK041(di)045:202: dug gsum las skyes gcong rong gsum //
NK041(di)045:203: bag chags las skyes gshed ma'i gzugs //
NK041(di)045:204: me chu gcan gzan 'jigs pa'i tshogs //
NK041(di)045:205: dkon mchog gsum la skyabs 'gro dang //
NK041(di)045:206: dge ba'i ram zlas dbugs 'byin shog /
NK041(di)045:207: dal 'byor tshang ba'i lus rten gyi //
NK041(di)045:208: mngal sgo bzang po 'dam pa dang //
NK041(di)045:209: smon lam dag pas mtshams sbyar nas //
NK041(di)045:210: mtho ris yon tan bdun ldan gyi //
NK041(di)045:211: rten la bla ma mnyes byas nas //
NK041(di)045:212: tshul bzhin spyod pa'i rang dbang dang //
NK041(di)045:213: ci gsung bka' bzhin bsgrub pa yis //
NK041(di)045:214: thugs yid gcig tu 'dres par shog //
